Uninstall skills (only way to stop using skills, removes from manifest and local installation)

Usage: fastskill remove [OPTIONS] [SKILL_IDS]...

Arguments:
  [SKILL_IDS]...  Skill IDs to remove

Options:
  -f, --force                    Force removal without confirmation
      --skills-dir <SKILLS_DIR>  Skills directory path
  -h, --help                     Print help

Uninstalls skills completely - this is the only way to stop using skills.
Removes from both local installation and project manifest (skill-project.toml).
Updates skills.lock to reflect the removal.

For manifest-managed projects: removes from [dependencies] and updates lock.
For local-only skills: removes from local installation only.

Examples:
  fastskill remove my-skill-id
  fastskill remove skill-a skill-b --force
